external_knowledge:
Eager explorers: researchers actively engaged in accessing molecular structures;
Molecules studied: refers to the count of unique molecular structures accessed by each researcher;
Typical clarity level: the average resolution of the molecular structures accessed by each researcher. The Protein (only) division pertains to the specific department in the mentioned query.

sql:
SELECT method_id, AVG(method_count) AS Average_Count
FROM structure_methods
GROUP BY method_id;
